Rating: 4
The first thing you have to realize about this recipe is that it's not for everyone. The cakes (and sauce) are supremely chocolate-y. If that makes you weak in the knees, then go ahead and make a big batch. If that makes you feel ill, don't make them. I think most people would prefer them as a brunch or dessert item, but I actually make them for breakfast. This will probably get me thrown off this board, but I usually don't make the chocolate sauce included here - instead, we pour a little Hershey's syrup on them. It's just easier and a lot less fattening. I know, a travesty...

