Rating: 2
We used Valrhona 70% bitter dark chocolate which made the recipe densely bitter. Thick batter made cooking difficult; recommend low temp and long duration to avoid charring. Weight and consistency is definitely closer to cake than a traditional pancake, as the name implies. In our opinion, definitely more of a dessert dish than brunch entree.

